P2433 【深基1-2】小学数学 N 合一

Written on December 26th, 2024 by ZJM 
#include<iostream>
#include<cstring>
#include<string>
#include<cstdio>
#include<cstdlib>
#include<algorithm>
#include<cmath>
#define For(k,i,j) for(int k=i;k<=j;k++)
using namespace std;
inline int read()
{
    char ch;
    int res=1;
    while((ch=getchar())<'0'||ch>'9') if(ch=='-') res=-1;
    res*=ch-48;
    while((ch=getchar())>='0'&&ch<='9')
        res=res*10+ch-48;
    return res;
}
int main()
{
	int n;
	cin>>n;
    if(n==1)
	{
        cout<<"I love Luogu!"<<endl;
    }
    if(n==2)
	{
        cout<<6<<" "<<4<<endl;
    }
    if(n==3)
	{
        cout<<3<<endl<<12<<endl<<2<<endl;
    }
    if(n==4)
	{
        cout<<166.666667<<endl;
    }
    if(n==5)
	{
        cout<<15<<endl;
    }
    if(n==6)
	{
        cout<<10.816653826391967879357663802411<<endl;
    }
    if(n==7)
	{
        cout<<110<<endl<<90<<endl<<0<<endl;
    }
    if(n==8)
	{
        cout<<31.41593<<endl<<78.539825<<endl<<523.59883333333333333333333333333<<endl;
    }
    if(n==9)
	{
        cout<<22<<endl;
    }
    if(n==10)
	{
        cout<<9<<endl;
    }
    if(n==11)
	{
        cout<<33.3333333333<<endl;
    }
    if(n==12)
	{
        cout<<13<<endl<<'R'<<endl;
    }
    if(n==13)
	{
        cout<<16<<endl;
    }
    if(n==14)
	{
        for(int i=1;i<=110;i++)
		{
            int s=120-i;
            int ans=s*i;
            if(ans==3500) 
			{
				cout<<i<<endl;
				break;
			}
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
